{{!
    @template filter_fastpix/unavailable

    Placeholder shown in place of a {fastpix:pb_<id>} shortcode when the
    referenced asset cannot be resolved (unknown, deleted, or cross-account) or
    cannot be embedded (DRM-protected). Renders no player and no interactive
    controls — see ADR-010 "Cross-account restore → Video unavailable UI".

    Context variables:
    * message - optional, an already-translated reason string. When absent, the
      generic "unavailable" string is shown.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "message": "This video is DRM-protected and cannot be played in an embed."
    }
}}
<div class="filter_fastpix-unavailable alert alert-warning" role="status">
    {{#message}}{{message}}{{/message}}
    {{^message}}{{#str}}unavailable, filter_fastpix{{/str}}{{/message}}
</div>
